sinit
________________________________________________________________________________

sinit is a simple init.  It was initially based on Rich Felker's minimal init.
There are 3 signals that sinit will act on - SIGUSR1 (powers off the machine),
SIGINT (reboots the machine) and SIGCHLD (reap childrens). [0]

Upstream: https://core.suckless.org/sinit/


[000] Index
________________________________________________________________________________

* Installation ........................................................... [001]
* Setup .................................................................. [002]
